## DESIGN TOKENS\
\
### Colors\
```css\
/* PRIMARY COLORS */\
--uct-blue: #003A70;           /* Main brand color - headers, accents, borders */\
--uct-blue-light: #2a5298;     /* Secondary blue - section titles, variations */\
--uct-blue-pale: #e8f4f8;      /* Notice bars, light backgrounds */\
--uct-blue-border: #d0e8f2;    /* Subtle borders */\
\
/* NEUTRAL COLORS */\
--background-gray: #f5f5f5;    /* Page background */\
--card-background: #f9f9f9;    /* Intro boxes, light sections */\
--info-background: #f8f9fa;    /* Info boxes */\
--white: #ffffff;              /* Cards, container */\
\
/* TEXT COLORS */\
--text-primary: #2c3e50;       /* Main body text */\
--text-secondary: #495057;     /* Intro text, descriptions */\
--text-muted: #555555;         /* List items, card text */\
--text-light: #666666;         /* Footer notes, details */\
\
/* ACCENT COLORS */\
--accent-red: #8B0000;         /* Special emphasis (GANs card, etc.) */\
