## ACCESSIBILITY NOTES\
\
1. **Color Contrast**\
   - UCT blue (#003A70) on white: WCAG AA compliant\
   - White text on UCT blue: WCAG AA compliant\
   - Ensure all text meets minimum contrast ratios\
\
2. **Font Sizes**\
   - Minimum body text: 1.05em (\uc0\u8776 16.8px)\
   - Headers clearly larger\
   - Readable at standard zoom levels\
\
3. **Semantic HTML**\
   - Use proper heading hierarchy (h1 \uc0\u8594  h2 \u8594  h3)\
   - Use semantic tags where appropriate\
   - Lists should use `<ul>` or `<ol>`\
\
4. **Alt Text**\
   - All images need alt text\
   - Decorative images: alt=""\
   - Meaningful images: descriptive alt text\
\
